mesen2 (2.1.1-1foundry1) resolute; urgency=medium

  * Initial Foundry Linux packaging of Mesen 2.1.1.
  * Repackage the upstream self-contained Linux x64 build (.NET AoT
    single-file); no source compile — upstream COMPILING.md requires the
    .NET 8 SDK + clang.
  * Declare the dlopen'd runtime deps (SDL2, X11 stack, libGL, fontconfig)
    that dh_shlibdeps cannot see inside the single-file bundle.
  * Skip dh_strip: the PublishSingleFile bundle appends native libs to the
    ELF host, so stripping/objcopy would truncate it. Upstream ships it
    stripped.
  * Upstream repo (SourMesen/Mesen2) is archived — no patches to forward.

 -- Foundry Linux <packages@foundrylinux.org>  Sun, 14 Jun 2026 06:08:54 +0700
